Quick Start!

# Dependencies

## Debian
$ sudo apt-get install libsdl2-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev

## Manjaro
$ sudo pacman -S sdl2 sdl2_ttf


# Build
$ make
$ ./battleship

# Controls
W and ARROW-UP        ==       MOVE UP
A and ARROW-LEFT      ==       MOVE LEFT
S and ARROW-DOWN      ==       MOVE DOWN
D and ARROW-RIGHT     ==       MOVE RIGHT

Q                     ==      ROTATE LEFT
E                     ==      ROTATE RIGHT

